OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1778069461
OL,3,CPrisoner still locked up 16 years
OL,4,Cafter three-year minimum sentence
OL,6,FJudges are being asked to review the
OL,7,Fcase of a man who remains in prison 16
OL,8,Fyears after he was given a three-year
OL,9,Fminimum sentence.
OL,11,FDaniel Grace, from West Yorkshire, was
OL,12,F19 when he was convicted at Leeds
OL,13,FCrown Court of wounding with intent in
OL,14,F2010.
OL,16,FHe was given a controversial
OL,17,Findeterminate sentence of detention
OL,18,Ffor public protection (DPP) and was
OL,19,Ftold he would have to spend at least
OL,20,Fthree years in custody.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
