FL,364,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1778069461
OL,3,CPrisoner still locked up 16 years
OL,4,Cafter three-year minimum sentence
OL,6,FSuch sentences, along with
OL,7,Fimprisonment for public protection
OL,8,Fsentences (IPPs), were abolished in
OL,9,F2012, but current inmates still have
OL,10,Fto obtain Parole Board approval to be
OL,11,Freleased.
OL,13,FGrace has been denied parole so far
OL,14,Fand an appeal against his sentence in
OL,15,F2020 failed.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/5
