CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1778069461
OL,3,CPrisoner still locked up 16 years
OL,4,Cafter three-year minimum sentence
OL,6,FHe has now had his sentence referred
OL,7,Fto the Court of Appeal by the Criminal
OL,8,FCases Review Commission (CCRC) - the
OL,9,Fseventh referral of its kind since the
OL,10,Fstart of the year as part of a wider
OL,11,Freview of such sentences.
OL,13,FA CCRC spokesperson said: "A review
OL,14,Fhas concluded that there is a real
OL,15,Fpossibility the Court of Appeal will
OL,16,Ffind that the sentencing judge made
OL,17,Ferrors in his assessment of Mr Grace's
OL,18,Ffuture risk and will therefore quash
OL,19,Fhis DPP sentence."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
