OL,3,CPrisoner still locked up 16 years
OL,4,Cafter three-year minimum sentence
OL,6,FMore than 150 other cases are being
OL,7,Finvestigated by a CCRC group looking
OL,8,Fat IPP and DPP sentences.
OL,10,FLast month the Court of Appeal has
OL,11,Fquashed six similar sentences, three
OL,12,Fof them following CCRC referrals.
OL,14,FCCRC chair Dame Vera Baird KC said:
OL,15,F"We welcome the Court of Appeal's
OL,16,Fdecision last month to quash six IPP
OL,17,Fand DPP sentences, three of them as a
OL,18,Fresult of CCRC referrals.
OL,26,@wD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/5
