FL,364,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1778069461
OL,3,CPrisoner still locked up 16 years
OL,4,Cafter three-year minimum sentence
OL,6,F"We look forward to the court's
OL,7,Freserved judgment for further clarity
OL,8,Fand guidance in approaching these
OL,9,Fcases.
OL,11,F"Again, anyone who is in a similar
OL,12,Fsituation and who has already lost
OL,13,Ftheir appeal is free to get in touch
OL,14,Fwith us about their case."
